# MIG Master

> Switch game backup tools, MIG Flash accessories, and setup gear

MIG Master is an online store focused on MIG Flash V2, MIG Flash Dumper, Switch-compatible accessories, chargers, adapters, and setup gear. The store helps customers compare products for personal Switch game backup workflows, card-based game switching, USB-C cartridge reading, and everyday Switch or Switch 2 accessory setups.

## Collections

- [首頁](https://migmaster.shop/a/shop/collections/frontpage): 首頁 is the homepage collection of MIG Master, featuring 5 products for Nintendo Switch.

## Products

- [MIG Flash Dumper — USB-C Game Cartridge Card Reader](https://migmaster.shop/a/shop/products/mig-flash-dumper): The MIG Flash Dumper is the perfect companion to the MIG Flash cart. While not required, the MIG Flash Dumper provides the most convenient and elegant way to back up your games.
- [Mig Flash V2 — Switch Game Backup Cartridge with Toggle Button](https://migmaster.shop/a/shop/products/mig-flash-v2): The Mig Flash V2 is a Switch game backup cartridge with a toggle button on the top for switching between games. It works the same as the original Mig Flash but includes a quality-of-life update: a quick press switches to the next game, a long press to the previous one.
